      <title>Re: Destructive Force AA</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=monkbalance&amp;message.id=11035#M11035</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;It lasts 6 seconds (1 tick) per rank, so at rank 3 it lasts the full duration of Inner Flame. It does 1 extra attack per main hand attack round on every mob within the AoE (including&amp;nbsp;the mob your attacking !!). So agro wise, it's just like attacking every mob around you slowly (single hits, but it's still reasonable agro), but it also helps up your DPS on the mob your attacking.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Down side is the very very long refresh time, and that it's also bad mojo to use if you chanter is mezzing !.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;When combined with IF and on a lot of mobs it can do major &lt;U&gt;total&lt;/U&gt; (combined) damage.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Jun 2006 12:52:52 GMT</pubDate>
